# Costs & API Limits

## What It Costs

| Pipeline | Estimated cost/run |
|----------|-------------------|
| PR Review | $4-6 |
| PR Answer | $3-5 |
| DoR / Estimation | $2-6 |
| Bug Fix | $11-15 |
| Dev Agent | $21-30 |

## Monthly Projections

| Scenario | Opus only | Mixed models |
|----------|----------|--------------|
| 5 PR reviews/week | ~$100 | ~$60 |
| + 3 DoR + Estimation/week | ~$150 | ~$80 |
| + 2 BugFix/week | ~$250 | ~$160 |
| Full (all agents active) | $400-550 | $300-420 |

## Built-in Safety

| Control | Setting |
|---------|---------|
| Daily rate limits | DoR: 20, PR Review: 50, PR Answer: 30, per-identity: 10 |
| Monthly token budget | Alerts at 80%, degrades at 90%, halts at 100% |
| Limits reset | Daily caps: midnight UTC. Monthly: 1st of month. |
| Config | Rate limits in `rate-limiter.js`. Token cap via `MONTHLY_TOKEN_CAP` pipeline variable. |

## Cost Optimization

- Use Sonnet/Haiku for read-only agents (DoR, Estimation, PR Review)
- Opus only for code-writing agents (BugFix, DevAgent)
- Prompt caching reduces input costs by 90% for cached context

